dcterms:description: A dataset comprising all possible Tic-Tac-Toe boards, including both legal and illegal configurations, along with corresponding conversations related to the board. This dataset serves as the foundation for training the model to perform tasks such as determining board validity, identifying the winner, and predicting the best move.
dcterms:title: Tic-Tac-Toe Dataset
